.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, rat, hamster, cat
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, librarian, manager, software-developer
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indonesian, italian, russian
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left or far right##3
2. the librarian is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the russian is on the left or right of the manager##3
4. the librarian is in an even position##4
5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the fisherman##1
6. the russian is on the right of the librarian##1
7. the indonesian is on the left of the librarian##1
8. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
9. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Pet      | goldfish                | cat  | rat | hamster   |
| Job           | software-developer | librarian | fisherman   | manager |
| Nationality   | indonesian         | dutch     | russian     | italian |

