.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, woodworking, collecting, rock-climbing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, mystery, satire, superhero
4 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig, hamster, lizard
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left##1
6. the person watching family movies is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
8. the owner of the lizard is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby      | collecting      | woodworking | video-games     | rock-climbing    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | family      | mystery | satire |
| Pet           | hamster   | guinea-pig  | cat     | lizard |

