2. the colombian is between the german and the person eating tomato##2
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left or far right##3
5. the colombian is on the left of the german##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
7. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating tomato is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | grapefruit | tomato  | cabbage   | lemon    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking  | woodworking     | traveling | singing |
| Nationality   | nigerian   | russian | colombian | german   |

