3. the person eating orange is on the far left##1
4. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating corn##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is the canadian##1
6. the person eating peas is on the right of the french##1
7. the french is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
8. the person eating orange is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
