.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, helicopter, skateboard, quad-bike
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, board-games, hiking, reading
4 different pets are kept: bird, horse, mouse, pony
1. the person driving the van is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is baking##2
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person driving the van##1
8. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Transport    | skateboard    | helicopter    | van  | quad-bike |
| Hobby   | reading | board-games | baking | hiking      |
| Pet     | horse   | bird        | pony   | mouse       |

 